<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 21:14:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据美国有线电视新闻网报道，中国习近平致电特朗普祝贺选举胜利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-called-trump-congratulate-election-victory-cnn-reports-2024-11-06/</link><description>据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 援引未透露姓名的消息人士报道，中国国家主席习近平周三致电唐纳德·特朗普，祝贺这位共和党人在美国总统大选中获胜。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 20:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-called-trump-congratulate-election-victory-cnn-reports-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>意大利就倍耐力可能违反治理行为启动针对中化集团的诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-opens-procedure-against-sinochem-over-pirelli-possible-governance-breach-2024-11-06/</link><description>倍耐力周三表示，意大利总理办公室对其最大股东中国中化集团启动了行政程序，理由是该公司可能违反了罗马为保护该轮胎制造商自主权而制定的规定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 19:37:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-opens-procedure-against-sinochem-over-pirelli-possible-governance-breach-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国供应商和进口商为特朗普承诺的关税做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-suppliers-importers-prepare-promised-trump-tariffs-2024-11-06/</link><description>一些美国企业正在启动计划，以保护自己的企业免受候任总统唐纳德·特朗普承诺对来自中国和墨西哥等美国最大贸易伙伴的大量商品征收新的、可能高额的关税的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:32:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-suppliers-importers-prepare-promised-trump-tariffs-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>对于欧洲市场来说，特朗普的回归给欧元带来痛苦，但债券却上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/europes-markets-trumps-return-spells-euro-pain-bond-gains-2024-11-06/</link><description>随着唐纳德·特朗普连任总统提高了征收高额关税的前景，投资者正准备迎接欧洲进一步的经济痛苦，这可能会加剧欧元的损失并损害其股市。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/europes-markets-trumps-return-spells-euro-pain-bond-gains-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>分析人士称，特朗普可能会加强伊朗石油立场，但很难阻止石油流向中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/trump-could-harden-iran-oil-stand-raise-china-ire-analysts-say-2024-11-06/</link><description>分析人士表示，前总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫可能意味着美国对伊朗实施更严厉的石油制裁，从而可能削减全球供应，但他的政府可能很难让伊朗最大的原油客户中国合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:19:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/trump-could-harden-iran-oil-stand-raise-china-ire-analysts-say-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的经济计划取决于减税、关税、移民打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-economic-plan-hinges-tax-cuts-tariffs-immigration-crackdown-2024-11-06/</link><description>美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将重新入主白宫，推出雄心勃勃的计划，包括广泛的进口关税、移民限制和额外减税，分析师认为这些计划将在短期内提振经济，但也会带来更大的预算赤字、疲弱的劳动力增长和更高的通胀。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-economic-plan-hinges-tax-cuts-tariffs-immigration-crackdown-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>郑重进WTA年终总决赛半决赛 雷巴基娜击败萨巴伦卡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-beats-paolini-march-into-wta-finals-semis-2024-11-06/</link><description>周三，中国选手郑钦文在利雅得举行的 WTA 年终总决赛中以 6-1 6-1 击败意大利四号种子茉莉花·保利尼，闯入半决赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-beats-paolini-march-into-wta-finals-semis-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺支持缅甸政治过渡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-pledges-support-myanmars-political-transition-2024-11-06/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国总理李强周三在会见缅甸军政府领导人时表达了北京对缅甸政治和解与过渡努力的支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:35:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-pledges-support-myanmars-political-transition-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>面对关税威胁，欧洲寻求安抚特朗普的选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/facing-tariff-threat-europe-eyes-options-appease-trump-2024-11-06/</link><description>欧盟正在考虑在唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫后安抚他的选择，因为欧盟正在准备恢复美国关税和其他贸易威胁，以及就如何对待中国进行艰难的交流。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:05:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/facing-tariff-threat-europe-eyes-options-appease-trump-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康中国区负责人被拘留，认为与保险调查无关</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-chinas-investigation-into-exec-separate-medical-insurance-probe-2024-11-06/</link><description>阿斯利康周三表示，其中国区总裁王亮已被中国当局拘留，虽然不清楚原因，但不认为这与涉及该公司的大型健康保险欺诈案有关。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-chinas-investigation-into-exec-separate-medical-insurance-probe-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥将受到特朗普胜利的初步打击，但仍有谈判空间</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-feel-initial-blow-trump-victory-has-room-negotiate-2024-11-06/</link><description>既然唐纳德·特朗普已经确保重返美国总统宝座，墨西哥就必须谨慎行事，但墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆仍然有谈判的空间，以减轻对贸易、移民和安全的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 12:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-feel-initial-blow-trump-victory-has-room-negotiate-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>马里诺队击败武里南，登上亚冠积分榜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/marinos-climb-asian-champions-league-standings-with-buriram-thrashing-2024-11-06/</link><description>周三，横滨水手队以 5-0 击败泰国 10 人武里南联队，这支日本球队在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛积分榜上升至第三位。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 12:39:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/marinos-climb-asian-champions-league-standings-with-buriram-thrashing-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>为何特朗普此次加征关税对中国经济构成更大威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/why-chinas-economy-is-more-vulnerable-trump-tariffs-this-time-2024-11-06/</link><description>当选下一任美国总统的唐纳德·特朗普威胁要对美国进口的中国商品征收 60% 的关税，这给世界第二大经济体带来了重大增长风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:28:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/why-chinas-economy-is-more-vulnerable-trump-tariffs-this-time-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>百乐嘉利宝 (Barry Callebaut) 预计可可豆价格不会回到 2022/2023 年水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/barry-callebaut-does-not-see-cocoa-bean-prices-returning-20222023-levels-2024-11-06/</link><description>瑞士巧克力制造商百乐嘉利宝 (Barry Callebaut) 周三表示，预计可可豆价格不会恢复到 2022/2023 年季节的水平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/barry-callebaut-does-not-see-cocoa-bean-prices-returning-20222023-levels-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫助手表示，德国汽车行业的困境显示出绿色转型的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/kremlin-aide-says-germany-car-industry-plight-shows-green-transition-risks-2024-11-06/</link><description>克里姆林宫的一位顾问周三表示，如果俄罗斯工业取代化石燃料的速度过快，俄罗斯工业可能会遭受德国汽车制造商的命运，德国汽车制造商已经裁掉了数万个工作岗位。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/kremlin-aide-says-germany-car-industry-plight-shows-green-transition-risks-2024-11-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>